HEADWORD: Gasometry
<hw>Gas*om"e*try</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The art or
practice of measuring gases; also, the science which treats of the
nature and properties of these elastic fluids.</def>
<rj><au>Coxe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

